<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>320</hymn_number>
<title>&quot;FEAR NOT&quot;</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Lau ki'n! Pathien na phaw
 Na kipahman lopi;
 A hat na'n A zotai,
 Lalpa na tha ahi!

[V2]
 Lau ki'n, A aw ahi,
 Na kawma thugen chuh;
 Dak inla, kipakin,
 Lal Isu Krista ah.

[V3]
 2. Lau ki'n! A man a zai,
 Na lungkhamna Aw chuh;
 A thu hinna tui chun,
 Na tha chau vang piena.

[V4]
 3. Lau ki'n! lungdawng hiel ki'n,
 Hun umpih zing ina;
 Hun panpih zel ina,
 Hun hihhat zel ina.

[V5]
 4. Lau ki'n! Lawi tawmte haw,
 Na Lalpau hungvak ding;
 Lopina latsak din,
 A Ina hun pui di'n.</lyrics>
</song>